=====================================================================================

As the devoutly single Don Johnston is dumped by his latest girlfriend, he receives 
an anonymous pink letter informing him that he has a son who may be looking for him. 
The situation causes Don to examine his relationships with women instead of moving 
on to the next one, and he embarks on a cross-country search for his old flames who 
might possess clues to the mystery at hand.
